      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything just keeps happening again. i try to fix things, i try to start over, but it’s always the same exact outcome. the same mistakes, the same loneliness, the same feeling of just being fundamentally broken. it feels like i'm just stuck in this loop that never actually goes anywhere.",
